---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="The Askesis Project" currentPage="/">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section style="position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
    <div class="wrapper" style="padding-top: 96px; padding-bottom: 120px;">
      <img src="/enso.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" class="enso-watermark" style="position: absolute; top: 50%; right: 40px; transform: translateY(-50%); width: 620px; height: 620px; object-fit: contain; pointer-events: none;" />
      <div style="position: relative; max-width: 760px;">
        <div style="font-family: 'Spline Sans Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.32em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #a35c41; margin-bottom: 30px;">ἄσκησις &nbsp;·&nbsp; áskēsis &nbsp;·&nbsp; to&nbsp;exercise</div>
        <h1 style="font-size: 78px; line-height: 1.04; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.018em; margin: 0 0 32px; text-wrap: balance;">Life as a practice,<br>not a project to be <em style="font-weight: 400;">optimized.</em></h1>
        <p style="font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.55; color: #4a443c; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 0 44px;">The consistent daily effort of shaping a mind, a body, and a character — on purpose. This began as the record of one person's midlife transformation. Here are the tools, and what they cost.</p>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px;">
          <a href="/practice" class="btn-primary">Work with me &nbsp;→</a>
          <a href="https://askesisproject.substack.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-outline">Read on Substack&nbsp;↗</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DEFINITION -->
  <section style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(26,23,20,0.10); background: #efe9dd;">
    <div class="wrapper" style="padding-top: 88px; padding-bottom: 88px;">
      <div class="definition-grid" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr; gap: 56px; align-items: start;">
        <div style="font-family: 'Spline Sans Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #6f675b; padding-top: 14px;">The word</div>
        <div style="max-width: 720px;">
          <p style="font-size: 30px; line-height: 1.45; font-weight: 400; margin: 0 0 28px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; text-wrap: pretty;">The Greek <em>ἄσκησις</em> comes from the verb <em>ἀσκέω</em> — to work, to exercise, to practice a craft with care. It came to mean a disciplined practice centered on shaping one's mind, body, and character.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.65; color: #4a443c; margin: 0; max-width: 600px;">This isn't asceticism. Not discipline disguised as denial. It is applied effort toward meaningful change — a process of becoming, repeated daily, with intention.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PILLARS -->
  <section>
    <div class="wrapper" style="padding-top: 96px; padding-bottom: 96px;">
      <div style="display: flex; align-items: baseline; justify-content: space-between; gap: 24px; margin-bottom: 56px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(26,23,20,0.12); padding-bottom: 22px;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 17px; font-family: 'Spline Sans Mono', monospace; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.04em; margin: 0; text-transform: uppercase; color: #1a1714;">Three lines of work</h2>
        <span style="font-family: 'Spline Sans Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; color: #6f675b; letter-spacing: 0.04em;">σῶμα · λόγος · ἦθος</span>
      </div>
      <div class="pillars-grid" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: rgba(26,23,20,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(26,23,20,0.12);">
        <div style="background: #f3efe6; padding: 40px 34px 46px; min-height: 280px;">
          <div style="font-family: 'Newsreader', serif; font-size: 40px; color: #a35c41; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1;">σῶμα</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 26px; font-weight: 500; margin: 0 0 6px; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">Movement</h3>
          <div style="font-family: 'Spline Sans Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #8a8175; margin-bottom: 18px;">Sōma · the body</div>
          <p style="font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4a443c; margin: 0;">A body kept in motion. Strength, breath, and the daily, unglamorous habit of training — the floor the rest is built on.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background: #f3efe6; padding: 40px 34px 46px; min-height: 280px;">
          <div style="font-family: 'Newsreader', serif; font-size: 40px; color: #a35c41; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1;">λόγος</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 26px; font-weight: 500; margin: 0 0 6px; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">Mind</h3>
          <div style="font-family: 'Spline Sans Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #8a8175; margin-bottom: 18px;">Lógos · reason</div>
          <p style="font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4a443c; margin: 0;">Attention trained like a muscle. Stoic clarity met with evidence — knowing what to hold and what to let pass.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background: #f3efe6; padding: 40px 34px 46px; min-height: 280px;">
          <div style="font-family: 'Newsreader', serif; font-size: 40px; color: #a35c41; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1;">ἦθος</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 26px; font-weight: 500; margin: 0 0 6px; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">Character</h3>
          <div style="font-family: 'Spline Sans Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #8a8175; margin-bottom: 18px;">Ēthos · the self</div>
          <p style="font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4a443c; margin: 0;">Who you become through repeated action. Not the resolution but the thousandth quiet act that makes it true.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OFFERINGS PREVIEW -->
  <section style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(26,23,20,0.10); background: #efe9dd;">
    <div class="wrapper" style="padding-top: 96px; padding-bottom: 96px;">
      <div style="max-width: 560px; margin-bottom: 56px;">
        <div style="font-family: 'Spline Sans Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #a35c41; margin-bottom: 20px;">Ways in</div>
        <h2 style="font-size: 44px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.015em; margin: 0; line-height: 1.1;">A practice is built, <em>not bought.</em></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="offerings-grid" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 28px;">
        <a href="/practice" class="offering-card" style="text-align: left; background: #f3efe6; border: 1px solid rgba(26,23,20,0.12); padding: 34px 30px 30px; color: inherit; display: flex; flex-direction: column; min-height: 240px; text-decoration: none;">
          <div style="font-family: 'Spline Sans Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; color: #8a8175; letter-spacing: 0.06em; margin-bottom: 26px;">01</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 25px; font-weight: 500; margin: 0 0 10px; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">1:1 Coaching</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4a443c; margin: 0 0 22px; flex: 1;">Private work, over months, to build a practice that holds when motivation doesn't.</p>
          <span style="font-family: 'Spline Sans Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.04em; color: #a35c41;">See how it works →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://askesisproject.substack.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="offering-card" style="text-align: left; background: #f3efe6; border: 1px solid rgba(26,23,20,0.12); padding: 34px 30px 30px; color: inherit; display: flex; flex-direction: column; min-height: 240px; text-decoration: none;">
          <div style="font-family: 'Spline Sans Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; color: #8a8175; letter-spacing: 0.06em; margin-bottom: 26px;">02</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 25px; font-weight: 500; margin: 0 0 10px; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">The Writing</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4a443c; margin: 0 0 22px; flex: 1;">Essays and weekly notes on discipline, movement, attention, and the work of becoming — free on Substack.</p>
          <span style="font-family: 'Spline Sans Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.04em; color: #a35c41;">Read on Substack →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SUBSTACK BAND -->
  <section style="background: #1a1714; color: #ece5d6;">
    <div class="wrapper" style="padding-top: 104px; padding-bottom: 104px;">
      <div class="substack-grid" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 64px; align-items: center;">
        <div>
          <div style="font-family: 'Spline Sans Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #c98a6e; margin-bottom: 22px;">The Writing</div>
          <h2 style="font-size: 46px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.015em; line-height: 1.1; margin: 0 0 18px;">The whole notebook<br>lives on Substack.</h2>
          <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; color: #b3aa9b; margin: 0; max-width: 440px;">Essays and weekly notes from inside the practice — what I'm training, reading, and getting wrong. Free to read. Subscribe to follow along.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 22px;">
          <img src="/enso.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" style="width: 88px; height: 88px; object-fit: contain; filter: invert(1); opacity: 0.85;" />
          <a href="https://askesisproject.substack.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-cream">Read on Substack&nbsp;↗</a>
          <span style="font-family: 'Spline Sans Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; color: #7d756a; letter-spacing: 0.04em;">askesisproject.substack.com</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
.offering-card:hover { border-color: rgba(26,23,20,0.45) !important; }

.enso-watermark { opacity: 0.8; }
@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .enso-watermark { opacity: 0.10; }
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .definition-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; gap: 28px !important; }
  .pillars-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
  .offerings-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
  .substack-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
}

@media (max-width: 640px) {
  h1 { font-size: 44px !important; line-height: 1.08 !important; }
}
</style>
